maven goals/ commands:
===================

1. mvn clean:  deletes target directory.

2. mvn compile: compile java code and create target folder with .class files(Byte code)

3. mvn test

4. mvn package: create jar file/ war file

5. mvn install

mvn package:  compile+test+package

mvn install: compile+test+package+install




